<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us</title>
  <style>
    .about-container {
      background-color: #1F2937;
      color: white;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .about-title {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .about-text {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: auto;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #3B82F6;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .about-img {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="about-container">
    <h2 class="about-title">About Us</h2>
    <p class="about-text">
      We are a company dedicated to <span class="highlight">cybersecurity</span>, <span class="highlight">artificial intelligence</span>, and <span class="highlight">custom decentralized application development</span>. We are committed to our work and our loyal clients vouch for us.
    </p>


    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mt-8">
      <a href="#contact" class="min-w-[150px] bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg transition duration-300 text-center">Contact</a>
      <a href="#quote" class="min-w-[150px] bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg transition duration-300 text-center">Request a Quote</a>
      <a href="#work-with-us" class="min-w-[150px] bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg transition duration-300 text-center">Work with Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
